<p>英 /əˈkjuːz/    美 /əˈkjuz/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>指责；控告；指控：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>the accused
被告</p></div>

<ul>
<li>accuse sb of (doing) sth:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The police accused him of theft. 
警方指控他犯有偷窃罪。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Germans are sometimes accused of not having a sense of humour. 
德国人有时受到诟病，被指缺乏幽默感。</p><footer>北师大⑤ – 13</footer></div></div>